-- Manchester United Agrees to Sign Borussia Dortmund’s Kagawa
-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 2012-06-05T08:30:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-05/manchester-united-agrees-to-sign-borussia-dortmund-s-kagawa.html
Manchester United agreed to sign
Borussia Dortmund’s Japanese midfielder Shinji Kagawa.  The transfer is subject to the 23-year-old passing a
medical test and obtaining a U.K. work permit, United said on
its website, without disclosing financial terms.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alex Duff at 
 aduff4@bloomberg.net  